author: MIKE HOUSEHOLDER and ED WHITE / AP
title: Hundreds Protest Michigan Governor’s Social Distancing Order by Rallying at the State Capitol
description: Hundreds of protesters drove past the Michigan Capitol on Wednesday to show their displeasure with Gov. Gretchen Whitmer’s COVID-19 orders.
content:
LANSING, Mich. — Hundreds of flag-waving, honking protesters drove past the Michigan Capitol on Wednesday to show their displeasure with Gov. Gretchen Whitmer’s orders to keep people at home and businesses locked during the coronavirus outbreak.
